The Extract for ${subtitle} '${title}' published by ${username} failed to refresh at ${completed_at}. 
% if notes.find('Invalid username or password') != -1:        
From our analysis, the cause is likely to be an invalid username or password. Full context is provided below for your reference.
% elif notes.find('INVALID_LOGIN') != -1:        
From our analysis, the cause is likely to be an invalid Salesforce login. Full context is provided below for your reference.
% elif notes.find('Unable to connect to the server') != -1:        
From our analysis, the likely cause is that the data source cannot connect to the server. Full context is provided below for your reference. 
% elif notes.find('The query time resource limit') != -1:        
From our analysis, the likely cause is that the duration of the extract exceeded the limits configured in your Tableau server. Full context is provided below for your reference.
% else:        
